{"tid":12354,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"新華社：張德江「充份肯定」幫港出聲","createTime":"2016-11-29T15:24:05.000Z","updateTime":"2016-11-29T16:06:45.000Z","uid":20933,"like":0,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"dc6ebc0e473ded22f97eb693628b879206e8e22c","tid":12354,"uid":20933,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-11-29T15:24:05.000Z","msg":"中國官方新華社晚上報道中共中央政治局常委、全國人大常委會委員長張德江，周二下午在人民大會堂會見了以周融為團長的香港「幫港出聲」訪京團，指張德江「認真聽取了訪京團的情況介紹」，充分肯定「幫港出聲」的工作，勉勵他們秉承為香港普通市民發聲的宗旨，積極反映民情，廣泛凝聚民意，弘揚愛國愛港主旋律，不斷增強社會正能量。<br />\n<br />\n報道指張德江強調，中央政府堅定不移維護國家主權、安全、發展利益和香港長期繁榮穩定，希望廣大香港同胞旗幟鮮明地反對「港獨」，共同維護香港社會政治穩定，切實把握國家發展機遇，凝心聚力謀發展、促和諧，推動香港「一國兩制」實踐不斷向前發展。<br />\n<br />\n翻查資料，「充份肯定」似乎是張德江的標準用語，張今年訪港時對梁特的工作評價，同樣是「充份肯定」。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"http://hkm.appledaily.com/detail.php?guid=55983125&amp;category_guid=6996647&amp;category=instant&amp;issue=2016112\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fhkm.appledaily.com%2Fdetail.php%3Fguid%3D55983125%26category_guid%3D6996647%26category%3Dinstant%26issue%3D2016112&d=goC%2B%2BwCxwRgX8SEPTes0uwT5PszEexF2%2B6H4LydsHP4%3D&h=a80cbedd\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=http%3A%2F%2Fhkm.appledaily.com%2Fdetail.php%3Fguid%3D55983125%26category_guid%3D6996647%26category%3Dinstant%26issue%3D2016112&h=4b912700\" target=\"_blank\">http://hkm.appledaily.com/detail.php?guid=55983125&amp;category_guid=6996647&amp;category=instant&amp;issue=2016112</a>"},{"pid":"53073f8fbdeb6535f3b60ef5533822a254da5dd4","tid":12354,"uid":30073,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-11-29T15:25:05.000Z","msg":"未死過<img src=\"/assets/faces/big/bomb.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/big/bomb.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/big/bomb.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"1d95e2fc041c26a09c254b1c03a0c621f339aec3","tid":12354,"uid":4942,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-11-29T15:26:13.000Z","msg":"又上去R維穩費"},{"pid":"cf7a2d9e20512c7cd690a33da3addee681d78d45","tid":12354,"uid":20933,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-11-29T16:02:32.000Z","msg":"OK"},{"pid":"800d7226a3cb04eac043463d7c4cbb53e3b39ea4","tid":12354,"uid":22858,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-11-29T16:05:21.000Z","msg":"佢唔見都無人記得鳩溶，而家係咪又想撥火 <img src=\"/assets/faces/big/photo.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/big/photo.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/big/photo.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"da544b1a3e082789f14a42cc786586d1ec961743","tid":12354,"uid":18739,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-11-29T16:06:14.000Z","msg":"張德江真係唔驚死<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"27e8b0254b0f7aee4a0cc959c5258329bbf65d91","tid":12354,"uid":349,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-11-29T16:06:45.000Z","msg":"張德肛：「Good boy」"}]}